1/31/96 v1.15

There are no packages anymore.  This should make it easier for others
to set up their own DynamicBillBoard because they no longer need
a BillBoard directory.

1/28/96 v1.13

FadeTransition does not work for image of greater then 64k pixels.  Made
an alternative class LargeImageFadeTransition for these images.

Added the new transition: RotateTransition class.

1/23/96 v1.10

Seems to be a problem with Netscape2.0b6 added a workaround until
I can figure out what is wrong.

v1.09

Found a bug that stops the images from being updated when running 
multiple instances of this applet.  Should be fixed.
